BookTrack
=========

A personal reading journal built with Ruby and Sinatra.
Track what you have read, what you are reading, and what is 
next on your list so you can get an idea of what you have done 
and what you need to be.

Built with Ruby, Sinatra, SQLite3, Puma, and ERB.

- This is a small learning project.
- For an overview of the project, see the `docs/` folder.
- I'm new to Ruby, so this project is experimental.
- The app stores data locally in `books.db`.
- No external services or APIs are required.
- See `docs/getting-started.md` for setup and run instructions.
